underlying_goal: To begin the process of porting a document template into a LaTeX style file.
primary_success: Correctly identified that using the existing ICLR style files would be a good starting point for the task.
brief_summary: The user initiated the task of porting a template to a LaTeX style file. Claude began by exploring the project to find existing templates and correctly identified a set of ICLR 2026 style files as a good foundation. The session ended after this initial exploration and planning phase.
